title: Lume Whole Body Women's Deodorant - Smooth Solid Stick - Aluminum Free - Soft Powder Scent - 2.6oz
product_description:
Smell better everywhere with Lume Whole Body Deodorant for Pits, Privates and Beyond.

Armpits aren’t the only place we have odor, and Lume is uniquely made to control ALL external body odor. One deodorant is all you need for underarms, underboobs, private parts, skinfolds and creases, belly buttons, and feet.

Our science based approach has raised the bar for personal hygiene. Lume Whole Body Deodorant for women is pH optimized to block odor before it starts. Certain traditional deodorants simply mask or neutralize odor after it forms.

Pair Lume Whole Body Deodorant for women with our Acidified Body Wash and Acidified Wipes, and you will be an odor free powerhouse from head to toe.

About Lume:
As a practicing OB/GYN with a deep understanding of women’s anatomy, body chemistry, and how detrimental body odor can be to confidence, Dr. Shannon Klingman had a suspicion that the common concern of odor below the belt was being overdiagnosed as Bacterial Vaginosis (BV). She discovered that the vagina is not usually to blame for day to day odor, and that women needed an external solution—not antibiotics or douches—to control external body odor in the right way.

Kitchen-made prototypes turned into clinically backed, outrageously effective deodorant designed to go where no others dare—anywhere body odor exists. And so, the first Whole Body Deodorant with 72 hour odor control was born.

The reflectors on the footrest allow for greater low-light visibility. Its lightweight steel frame is sturdy, but not a burden to carry around. The swivel wheel can unlock for low speed maneuvering or be locked back into place for jogging.

The Expedition Jogger is one of the safest and most comfortable ways for you and your baby to enjoy an expedition together.
